  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hop into Adventure: Discover \"BUNNY\"</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"BUNNY\" is a side-scrolling action game where Bunny and Smallbird embark on an adventure to find their friends. Control Bunny as you navigate through stages, overcoming obstacles and squeezing through walls. There's no game over, so everyone can play through to the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/f8b3ebd1cdc12cd09cad65d032b7d85d.poster.avif?t=1747859500\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/f8b3ebd1cdc12cd09cad65d032b7d85d.webm?t=1747859500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/f8b3ebd1cdc12cd09cad65d032b7d85d.mp4?t=1747859500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For the Busy You: Enjoy a Game Experience in Just 15 Minutes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is perfect for those looking to enjoy a quick gaming experience, as it can be completed in just 15 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover Friends Across 4 Unique Courses!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each course consists of three engaging parts, offering a total of four unique courses to explore and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/16b70e3937cb50afc00007c06b9a2f14.avif?t=1747859500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras_big/16b70e3937cb50afc00007c06b9a2f14.avif?t=1747859500 width=800 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy Controls: Perfect for Beginners!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's easy to operate with just a stick and two buttons, making it accessible for even the youngest players to enjoy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/d22ec359340c44d4a12f75d2b409879e.avif?t=1747859500\" width=566 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Fun After Completing the Game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you clear the game, various bonus features and lighthearted scenes will be unlocked based on your points, so you can continue to enjoy the game even after clearing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/2f744cb4bb4133c88528bdd813c24869.avif?t=1747859500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras_big/2f744cb4bb4133c88528bdd813c24869.avif?t=1747859500 width=800 height=132 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hop into Adventure: Discover \"BUNNY\"</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"BUNNY\" is a side-scrolling action game where Bunny and Smallbird embark on an adventure to find their friends. Control Bunny as you navigate through stages, overcoming obstacles and squeezing through walls. There's no game over, so everyone can play through to the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/f8b3ebd1cdc12cd09cad65d032b7d85d.poster.avif?t=1747859500\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/f8b3ebd1cdc12cd09cad65d032b7d85d.webm?t=1747859500\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/f8b3ebd1cdc12cd09cad65d032b7d85d.mp4?t=1747859500\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>For the Busy You: Enjoy a Game Experience in Just 15 Minutes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is perfect for those looking to enjoy a quick gaming experience, as it can be completed in just 15 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Discover Friends Across 4 Unique Courses!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each course consists of three engaging parts, offering a total of four unique courses to explore and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/16b70e3937cb50afc00007c06b9a2f14.avif?t=1747859500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras_big/16b70e3937cb50afc00007c06b9a2f14.avif?t=1747859500 width=800 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Easy Controls: Perfect for Beginners!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's easy to operate with just a stick and two buttons, making it accessible for even the youngest players to enjoy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/d22ec359340c44d4a12f75d2b409879e.avif?t=1747859500\" width=566 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Fun After Completing the Game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you clear the game, various bonus features and lighthearted scenes will be unlocked based on your points, so you can continue to enjoy the game even after clearing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras/2f744cb4bb4133c88528bdd813c24869.avif?t=1747859500\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789140/extras_big/2f744cb4bb4133c88528bdd813c24869.avif?t=1747859500 width=800 height=132 /></span></p>",
